  <brief_title>Safety and Efficacy of Endocuff-assisted Colonoscopy for Adenoma Detection.</brief_title>
  <official_title>Endocuff-assisted Colonoscopy: a Randomized Back-to-back Colonoscopy Study of Adenoma Detection.</official_title>
  <sponsors>
